The following directories and files contain code derived from DMax (Apache-2.0):
  dFactory/tasks/train_t3_dmax_bd_oput.py
    - block_diffusion_mask attention construction
    - argument dataclasses (LLaDA2ModelArguments, LLaDA2DataArguments,
      LLaDA2TrainingArguments) and main training loop scaffolding
    - dataset loading, FSDP2 setup, optimiser/scheduler/checkpoint plumbing
  dFactory/configs/sft/t3_llada2_mini_bd_oput_*.yaml
    - YAML structure and field names
  dFactory/models/llada2_moe/modeling_llada2_moe.py  (modified in place)
    - LLaDA2MoeSparseMoeBlock.__init__ branch on model_type: changed from strict
      equality with "llada2_moe_veomni" to a suffix match so that derived configs
      such as "think_talk_llada2_veomni" also pick up the fused-experts layout.
      Marked with a "# T3-D MODIFIED:" comment at the modification site.

The following files contain code vendored from Think-Then-Talk (internal):
  dFactory/models/think_talk_llada2/modeling_think_talk_llada2.py
    - TalkModel block construction patterns (gated residual injection, fuse_representation
      hook, anchor RPS state update)
    - prune_last_n_blocks helper (used by ablation A1.5)

Where DMax or Think-Then-Talk code has been modified, the change is marked with an
"# T3-D MODIFIED:" or "# T3-D ADDED:" comment so the diff is auditable.
